Actress Annie Idibia has stated she and her husband just renewed their marital vows. The music star’s wife explained the renewal of marital vows was done as part of the celebrations for their 10th wedding anniversary. The 37-year-old ‘Young, Famous and African” reality star made this known in a post on her Instagram page where she disclosed the ceremony was privately done but promised to share videos and photos from it soonest. The post reads: “Yes fam, a guy and I renewed our vows. 10 years anniversary. Was very intimate. But we also wanted to share it with the whole world.   Tacha, Made Kuti bag endorsement deal     God’s love gifted me Austin Faani – Chacha Eke     I look better than most Nigerian girls – Bobrisky   “VULNERABILITY Isn’t Weakness! I Wanna Believe That It Is being BRAVE … It IS “STRENGTH” “Annie Macaulay Idibia xoxo. Will definitely post images from our 2nd very intimate wedding/vows renewal #anniemacaulayidibia #annieidibia #youngfamousandafrican.” “A guy and I only showed a very tiny bit of the wedding! I know we owe u guys at least a one min visuals and images!! Will post soonest!”.